套用模板：

```
class Solution:
    def search(self, nums: List[int], target: int) -> int:
        if not nums:
            return -1
        left, right = 0, len(nums) - 1
        while left + 1 < right:
            mid = (left + right) // 2
            if nums[mid] < target:
                left = mid
            elif nums[mid] > target:
                right = mid
            else:
                return mid
        if nums[left] == target:
            return left
        if nums[right] == target:
            return right
        return -1
```
